00:56:49.962 --> 00:56:52.442
programs into the clinic. So I'm really excited to tell you today about what we've

972
00:56:52.482 --> 00:56:53.502
been doing at Senti Bio.

973
00:56:54.602 --> 00:56:57.402
Senti Bio is a biotech company based in the San Francisco Bay Area.

974
00:56:58.572 --> 00:57:01.662
So what Senti has been working on is developing a class of

975
00:57:01.702 --> 00:57:05.662
technologies for more precise cancer targeting, and we call

976
00:57:05.722 --> 00:57:09.562
these technologies logic gates. So the idea is, can you take a cell

977
00:57:09.602 --> 00:57:13.552
and program it to recognize and kill cancer cells more specifically, and at

978
00:57:13.562 --> 00:57:17.252
the same time, recognize healthy cells and protect those healthy cells from being

979
00:57:17.282 --> 00:57:17.542
killed?

980
00:57:18.452 --> 00:57:21.972
We've developed this logic gate technology for the last few years, and now have

981
00:57:22.002 --> 00:57:24.271
